title: One Bedroom Meadows apartment available now!
posting_body: ['Beach South at the Lake is a premier community professionally managed by Bigos Property Management.', 'We now offer online virtual tours on our website as well as in-person self-guided tours.', 'We have our Meadows 1 bedroom 1 bathroom available now for a move in!', 'We offer lease lengths ranging from 3-13 months.', 'Our apartments feature a balcony or patio, dishwasher, refrigerator, stove, microwave, excellent closet space, and lots of natural light.', 'All utilities are included except electric and cable/internet.', 'Beach South is a pet friendly community (breed restrictions apply).', 'Our community offers large amounts of outdoor space for you and your pet!', 'We are conveniently located on Twin Lake, which is near downtown Robbinsdale off of Hwy 100 and France Avenue North.', 'Please visit our website at <URL> or call', 'show contact info', 'ext. 0', 'for availability, pictures, and pricing.', '*Please note, pricing is subject to change daily.', 'Adjusting your move-in date or lease terms will affect pricing.', 'Payment of a $45 application fee will lock in the rental rate for only the selected lease term and move-in date.', "Don't miss your opportunity to apply for this spacious apartment; it will go fast!"]
